The evidence with the title 'A surge of state abortion restrictions puts providers— and the ... ' says Over the past three years, however, a startling number of states have passed harsh new restrictions . In 2011–2013, leg- islatures in 30 states enacted 205 abortion Restric- tions— more than the total number enacted in the entire previous decade ( see chart, page 10).1 No year from 1985 through 2010 saw more than 40 . 
